div><div class=\"mt-20\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"glass p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8 h-fit\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-electric-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center text-electric-blue\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hash\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"9\" y2=\"9\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"15\" y2=\"15\"></line><line x1=\"10\" x2=\"8\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"16\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">Generator Settings</h3></div><form class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-grey font-bold\">Content Topic</label><select class=\"w-full bg-midnight-lt border border-white/10 p-4 text-white focus:border-electric-blue/50 outline-none appearance-none\"><option value=\"business\" selected=\"\">Business &amp; Entrepreneurship</option><option value=\"tech\">Technology &amp; Startups</option><option value=\"fashion\">Fashion &amp; Style</option><option value=\"fitness\">Fitness &amp; Health</option><option value=\"restaurant\">Food &amp; Restaurants</option><option value=\"education\">Education &amp; Learning</option><option value=\"beauty\">Beauty &amp; Makeup</option><option value=\"travel\">Travel &amp; Tourism</option></select></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-grey font-bold\">Platform</label><select class=\"w-full bg-midnight-lt border border-white/10 p-4 text-white focus:border-electric-blue/50 outline-none appearance-none\"><option value=\"instagram\" selected=\"\">Instagram</option><option value=\"tiktok\">TikTok</option><option value=\"linkedin\">LinkedIn</option><option value=\"twitter\">Twitter / X</option></select></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-grey font-bold\">Post Type</label><select class=\"w-full bg-midnight-lt border border-white/10 p-4 text-white focus:border-electric-blue/50 outline-none appearance-none\"><option value=\"general\" selected=\"\">General Post</option><option value=\"promo\">Promotion / Sale</option><option value=\"education\">Educational</option><option value=\"event\">Event / News</option><option value=\"behind\">Behind the Scenes</option></select></div></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full bg-white text-midnight py-5 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-electric-blue hover:text-white transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg> Generate Hashtags</button></form></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-midnight-mid border border-white/5 p-8 md:p-10 min-h-[300px] flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-electric-blue/5 blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6 relative z-10\"><h4 class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-electric-blue font-bold flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-camera\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.997 4a2 2 0 0 1 1.76 1.05l.486.9A2 2 0 0 0 18.003 7H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1.997a2 2 0 0 0 1.759-1.048l.489-.904A2 2 0 0 1 10.004 4z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"13\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg> Generated Set</h4></div><div class=\"flex-1 relative z-10\"><div class=\"h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center space-y-4 pt-8\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-grey/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hash\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"9\" y2=\"9\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"15\" y2=\"15\"></line><line x1=\"10\" x2=\"8\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"16\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg></div><p class=\"text-grey text-xs italic\">Adjust settings and click generate</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-midnight-lt/30 border border-white/5 p-6 flex gap-4 items-start\"><div class=\"mt-1 text-grey/40\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Platform Note</p><p class=\"text-grey text-xs leading-relaxed\">Instagram allows up to 30 hashtags. We recommend using 10-15 highly relevant ones for maximum reach.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-32 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">The Science of Hashtags</h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed\">In 2026, hashtags aren&#x27;t just for decoration—they are a metadata signal that helps AI-driven algorithms categorize your content. Using the right mix of broad and niche hashtags ensures your posts are shown to the people most likely to engage with your brand in Nigeria.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 pt-8 text-left\"><div class=\"p-8 bg-midnight-mid border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/30 transition-colors\"><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-3 tracking-tight text-lg\">Algorithm Sync</h4><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed\">Our logic aligns with the latest platform-specific limits and categorization preferences for 2026.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 bg-midnight-mid border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/30 transition-colors\"><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-3 tracking-tight text-lg\">Local Relevance</h4><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed\">Includes high-engagement Nigerian tags like #LagosEats or #TechNigeria based on your selected niche.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 bg-midnight-mid border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/30 transition-colors\"><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-3 tracking-tight text-lg\">Intent Based</h4><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed\">Whether you&#x27;re educating or selling, we add modifiers that signal your post&#x27;s purpose to the platform.</p></div></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hephzibah Media Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:tr